Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有什麼預定的事要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴  怎麼感覺你那麼小而且還很像貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一醒來就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有耳朵  狗耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然還有尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排你沒什麼吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸什麼時候能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什麼時候能回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那人真是一去不復返啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.45,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（ハツ 牛，雞，豬等食用動物心臟的俗稱，用語烤雞肉串等。\N由於這裡家的名字都是跟雞的食物有關故此翻譯）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是乾炸的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小鈴變成了像動物的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心它們卻成為了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先去村子看看瞄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 得找到能好好地解釋這現象的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是熊熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  行行  早安
